header.title: Day-ahead prices
header.questionMarkInfo:
Day-ahead prices represent the result of Nord Pools day-ahead implicit auction market.

 

Between 2012-06-18 and 2013-06-03:

ELE: The Estonian Latvian Exchange Area handles import/export on the cross border between Estonia and Latvia. 

 

Peak = 08:00 to 20:00

Off peak 1 = 00:00 to 08:00

Off peak 2 = 20:00 to 00:00

Average = arithmetic average
